:name:
Synergy (ability)

:coretxt:
Choose one ability. 
You are extremely comfortable when using this ability.
You are learned to use it with such ease that you can combine it with other ability when they are able to support each other.
Whenever you are able to use this ability and some other ability you can add supporting ability as bonus dice (without check).
You can learn synergy multiple times but you can never add bonus dice from several abilities.

:cost:
1 from related pool

:tags:
Universal
